                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17690906-107-defend998 t17690906-107-punish568"></join>
               Imprisoned
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Compare these with No. 22, and No. 129, in this Mayoralty, and No. 640, in Mr. Alderman Harley's Mayoralty, and the old stale trick, which is newly revived of pricking in the belt, No. 479, in Mr. Alderman Blachford's Mayoralty.</p>
